For information on installing from source, get r3r-<version>.tar.gz and then
read the file BUILDING.

For installing on x86 Linux, run r3r-<version>.x86.package.  See
<http://autopackage.org/docs/howto-install/> if you need help installing it.

For installing on Windows, run r3r-<version>.exe.

These files can be found at
<http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=90897>.
